  "texts": [
    "The correct implementation of Chat-GPT notably improved students' critical thinking skills.",
    "Another study conducted by Exintaris et al. (2023, pp. 4-7) explored the integration of ChatGPT with metacognitive scaffolding, problem-solving practice, and analysis of ChatGPT responses.",
    "It demonstrated that by incorporating ChatGPT into the critical thinking process, participants were able to identify possible dos and don'ts when using GAI.",
    "The approach prompted students to critically engage with both the content and ChatGPT's feedback, thereby cultivating a deeper understanding and analytical outlook on the subject matter.",
    "As students expressed a growing inclination towards employing ChatGPT for critical thinking and recommended its usage, the study highlighted that identifying the essential task of identifying the limitations of generative AI as a foundational element in educator preparation."
